        <front>
            <titlePage type="titlepage" n="1" rendition="#manuscript">
                <docTitle>
                    <titlePart type="main" rend="purple_ink white_paper" rendition="#manuscript">The
                        president is Gone</titlePart>
                    <titlePart type="sub" rend="black ink white_paper" rendition="#manuscript">And
                        other notes<lb/>from the future</titlePart>
                </docTitle>
                <docAuthor rend="black ink white_paper">
                    <persName>Angélica</persName>
                </docAuthor>
                <docDate rend="black ink white_paper">2023</docDate>
            </titlePage>
        </front>

        <body>
            <div1 n="2" rendition="#manuscript" rend="purple_ink white_paper">
                <!-- When the rend is the same on all the page,
                I used it on the element that englobe all my paragraphes.-->
                <p>The president<lb/>is gone.</p>
                <p>And the vice<lb/>president is gone<lb/> too.</p>
                <p>We created a <lb/>world where</p>
                <p> we didn't need <lb/>these false idols.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="3" rendition="#manuscript" rend="purple_ink white_paper">
                <p>The priest is gone.<lb/> The missionaries are <lb/>all gone too.</p>
                <p>We didn't need them <lb/>telling us what to do.</p>
                <p>We decided to do some <lb/>thinking for ourselves.</p>
                <p>So now</p>
                <p>The police are gone,</p>
                <p>The <choice>
                        <orig>sherrifs</orig>
                        <corr>sheriff</corr>
                    </choice> and <lb/>deputies and hey <lb/>the criminals are <lb/>all gone
                    too.</p>
                <p>Theres no jails and<lb/> no prisons, no heartless</p>
                <p><lb/>warehouses full of <lb/>people, living breathing.</p>
                <p><lb/>We didn't want those things <lb/>anymore. So we</p>
                <p><lb/>Got rid of all our bosses,<lb/> we all quit our "jobs"</p>
                <p><lb/>and realized we could actually find our purpose...</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="4" rendition="#manuscript" rend="purple_ink pink_paper">
                <p><lb/>We got <lb/>rid of the <lb/>Landlords ... it</p>
                <p><lb/>wasn't there land <lb/>to "lord" anyway ...</p>
                <p><lb/>and we got rid of <lb/>renters too.</p>
                <p><lb/>Now were all just <lb/>livers... livers ?</p>
                <p><lb/>Haha ... I mean were <lb/>all people who get <lb/>to be alive,</p>
                <p><lb/>People who get <lb/>to experience our <lb/>world</p>
                <p><lb/>and not just <lb/>fight to survive it.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="5" rendition="#manuscript">
                <!-- Here the color change on the same page, so I used my rend attribute on every paragraphe-->
                <p rend="purple_ink pink_paper"><lb/>So we got rid of <lb/>the corporations.
                    <lb/>That's right.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink pink_paper"><lb/>Now <lb/>the CEOs are gone <lb/>and the
                    shareholders <lb/>and investors and <lb/>even the consumers are gone too.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper"><lb/>We got rid <lb/>of them when</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper"><lb/>They were <lb/>treating the <lb/>rest of the
                    <lb/>world like a <lb/>game ...</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper"><lb/>They <lb/>played by unfair <lb/>rules...</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper"><lb/>So we burned <lb/>the rule book</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper"><lb/>And the game board, <lb/>all the cards and
                    <lb/>the dice,</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper"><lb/>and we got rid <lb/>of the markets <lb/>and
                    the money and</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper"><lb/>we started valuing <lb/>people ...animals
                    ...plants ... <lb/>the world ...</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper"><lb/>For what they are :</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">Gifts ... Blessigngs ... <lb/>not from any <lb/>of
                    us ... <lb/>to all of us ...</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper"><lb/>Gifts.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="6" rendition="#manuscript" rend="purple_ink white_paper">
                <p><lb/>So we got rid <lb/>of the food prices <lb/>and the "cost" of healthcare
                    and</p>
                <p><lb/>decided to live in <lb/>abundance. We <lb/>stopped putting a <lb/>price tag
                    on life.</p>
                <p><lb/>So we got rid of <lb/>the rich. And we <lb/>got rid of the <lb/>poor. We
                    decided <lb/>that we all could <lb/>do more...</p>
                <p>We got rid of <lb/>the borders and <lb/>walls... The binary <lb/>structures that
                    kept <lb/>us apart...</p>
                <p>We realized <lb/>how fragile they were, <lb/>how easily they could
                    <lb/>crumble.</p>
                <p>They <lb/>didn't <lb/>stand <lb/>a <lb/>chance <lb/>against <lb/>the power we had
                    ...</p>
                <p><lb/>That we still have.</p>
                <p><lb/>The power of love ... <lb/>creativity ...solidarity</p>
                <p><lb/>We never once surrendered.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="7" rendition="#manuscript" rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">
                <p><lb/>So now the hatred <lb/>is gone. <lb/>The silence and <lb/>shame too.</p>
                <p><lb/>We got rid <lb/>of them; we <lb/>loved to hard !</p>
                <p><lb/>In the best way <lb/>possible. We <lb/>embodied our truths.</p>
                <p><lb/>We didn't let lies <lb/>stop us. So we <lb/>got rid of the <lb/>mass media
                    and <lb/> the legislators are <lb/>all gone too !</p>
                <p>We got rid <lb/>of the teachers, there <lb/>are no more of them <lb/>and we got
                    rid of <lb/>the students too.</p>
                <p>We realized we have <lb/><emph>lots</emph> more fun when <lb/>we all become
                    <lb/>learners, creators, participants <lb/>in our reality and <lb/>not mere
                    predefined roles.</p>
                <p><lb/>And we were so <lb/>successful ! <lb/>We still are.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="8" rendition="#manuscript" rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">
                <p><lb/>And now the <lb/>violence is all <lb/>gone,</p>
                <p><lb/>and the <lb/>tanks and guns <lb/>are gone too.</p>
                <p><lb/>The gas is gone, <lb/>the bombs, the <lb/>chemicals they <lb/>dumped into
                    the <lb/>earth our home.</p>
                <p><lb/>They are all gone.</p>
                <p><lb/><emph>We got rid of them !</emph></p>
                <p><lb/><emph>Chose life,</emph></p>
                <p><lb/>Chose love, chose connection <lb/>instead of fear.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="9" rendition="#manuscript" rend="purple_ink, blue surgical mask">
                <p><lb/>We chose <lb/>each other. <lb/>And we still <lb/>do. That's <lb/>how we
                    <lb/>made it so <lb/>far.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="10" rendition="#manuscript" rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">
                <p><lb/>But we looked <lb/>beyond ourselves <lb/>too and we chose <lb/>the world,
                    again <lb/>as it is, gifts, <lb/>glorious and <lb/>abundant and <lb/>we realized
                    we had <lb/>so much we were <lb/>missing.</p>
                <p><lb/>So we <lb/>don't have the <lb/>scarcity the <lb/>fear and coercion <lb/>any
                    more.</p>
                <p><lb/>No more <lb/>extraction and <lb/>expansion and <lb/>exploitation <caesura/>
                    <lb/>that's all gone. <lb/>We embraced <lb/>cycles <lb/>and <lb/>transitions,
                    <lb/>trangressions, <lb/>transformations,</p>
                <p>We got rid <lb/>of control <lb/>and welcomed <lb/>in community. <lb/>And we
                    thrive, <lb/>and we thrive, <lb/>and we thrive, <lb/><emph>and we
                    thrive.</emph></p>
            </div1>
        </body>
